　華　　民　　國　　111 　年　　8 　　月　　22　　日","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/PCDM/111%2c%e8%81%b2%2c1950%2c20220819%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"PCDM,111,聲,1950,20220819,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"聲","JNO":"1950","JDATE":"20220819","JTITLE":"定其應執行刑"}